__TOC__


To ensure the wider Ubuntu community knows what different people are working on, teams are expected to provide short monthly reports of what they are working on. This helps us all know what the project as a whole is working on.

'''If your team is not producing monthly reports, see <nowiki>[[BuildingCommunity-TeamReporting|this page]]</nowiki> to get your team started.'''

=== Reports ===

If you are starting a new month's report, use <nowiki>[[TeamReports-MonthTemplate|this template]]</nowiki>.
